room_title: Escape room "Arizona Sunshine VR" by 13th Gate Escape in Baton Rouge
room_address: 800 St Phillip St, Baton Rouge, LA 70802
room_description: Based off the award-winning and best-selling VR shooter, Arizona Sunshine LB VR offers an untethered VR experience that transports 2-4 players straight into the heart of a zombie apocalypse. Freely move around and interact with each other in one real-world space using full-body tracking, 4D effects, and a range of weaponry.Can your squad hold out long enough to set a new record against the brain-hungry undead?
